lead_paragraph: Poland striker Arek Milik has moved from Ajax Amsterdam to Napoli for 35 million Euros ($39 million), his management group said on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Napoli Sign Poland Forward Milik From Ajax
headline.main: Napoli Sign Poland Forward Milik From Ajax
